UsageCost: $10 for full charge plus $5 per person to camp and use facilities
GeneralComments:
Please call first - leave a message if no answer as coverage can be patchy.
Three acres of gardens in Glenbervie, a great spot to stop off overnight. There are numerous grassy enclaves nestled between hundreds of mature trees. One standard 15a caravan socket plus 10a three pin available. Bring your tent or book our unit on airbnb. Guest toilet and shower facilities adjacent to charge point; barbecue available for cooking in the garden.
